{"tid":219421,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"秦始皇","createTime":"2017-04-27T08:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T00:50:38.000Z","uid":9330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc6dd1f8fac392fd04aa280166a77e23c9cd842","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"曾經我以為自己回到過去就可以改變一切<br />\n點知原來我所做既一切都只係歷史既一部分<br />\n當我知道左我叫嬴政既時候，我同自己講我一定唔會係歷史上既嗰個暴君，但係我無得揀，我都係焚書坑儒，我都係捉平民百姓修築長城，我都係派人搵仙丹，妄想長生不老，我始終都搵人起左屬於我既陵墓，所有有參與我陵墓既人都同我陪葬⋯⋯"},{"pid":"c3121a85e835be73f228086738da57c148ad6fcc","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"隨筆寫一寫 文筆差  唔好鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f957ef580ff39f940afb3eabadba11af8aee0d9","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"「趙高，辛苦你啦，要為朕背負千古罵名。」<br />\n「陛下呢個係奴才既榮幸！」<br />\n「扶蘇看似賢能，但只係蒙恬既一個傀儡，民間呼聲太大，滿朝文武朕已經壓唔住，朕只可立扶蘇為二世，朕一死，到時候就靠你撥亂反正啦。」<br />\n「陛下...」只見一個陰柔既男人眼中有涙水打轉。<br />\n「趙高，朕當初一統六國，何等意氣風發，如今看似威風，但竟然只有你可信，連李斯...算啦 到時你用功名利祿威逼李斯幫你殺扶蘇，立胡亥為帝。」<br />\n「奴才遵旨！」<br />\n「退下啦。」話畢，一個身穿太監服既男人走岀左宮殿。<br />\n「世人都以為寡人想長生不老覓仙丹，就連寡人穿越前都以為係，又有邊個知所謂既仙丹只係藉口，朕只係佈局尋死，假扮自然死亡，以推翻我建立既帝國...我既然可以統一六國，成就大秦，亦可以將佢毀滅...」一個男人身穿一件黑色繡滿龍圖案既袍喃喃自語道...."},{"pid":"85b9836da2e08c31ff5d026b2256c35c15a97f28","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f32f03e417a8d22271e493738215dc841864270","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"一個太監將兩人帶到皇上前面，<br />\n「陛下，您要既人奴才已經帶到，奴才先行告退。」<br />\n當太監離開後，秦始皇打量眼前兩個人一段時間，終於開口，「朕要你地兩個改名換姓潛伏民間，成為農民，朕死後，時機一到反我大秦，你兩個可願意？」<br />\n「臣...不敢，臣等永遠忠於大秦，忠於皇上！」兩個聲音同時一齊發岀。<br />\n「朕知道，就係因為咁先要你地咁做，你地到時嗌住王侯將相，寧有種乎，反我大秦，只有咁做先可以保我大秦血脈，秦塵港、秦悟星你地可接我呢道旨意？」<br />\n「臣等接旨！臣秦塵港/秦悟星今改名為陳勝/吳廣，為我大秦效力。」<br />\n「願我大秦千秋萬代，永世不朽！」<br />\n商談一輪後秦塵...陳勝、吳廣帶住狂熱既眼神，離開了宮殿，只留下秦始皇一人在殿中會心微笑：「季兄，我留落在外既同胞兄弟，路我已經為你鋪好，呢個天下就交俾你啦，希望你唔好令我失望。」"},{"pid":"885bebb7fa26daba3a9efa06595905eb65a4f0a8","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac5a08eef0a20b6c09c19e5b950d36b9034e77b","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0412034691396c3beceda60fe2c7bcf3622768","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beeccdb09580478e18073880d7beb07639f79bba","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"有人入黎睇 我再繼續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5645d1824e9de02df8399da6bc3cc58fd4c4be56","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce61a594f5e4afdca51dd5bb2f52a35760c3aef7","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb08638fd443a157c4e0a19cc7e83df0b461957b","tid":219421,"uid":20495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d8dc36243c4daeacea96782336fb095b395fee","tid":219421,"uid":9330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}